# Supabase
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# App
VITE_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173
# Sentry client-side DSN (optional). Leave blank locally to disable Sentry.
# Set in Vercel env for production so client crashes are captured. Safe to
# expose in the bundle — a DSN is an ingest-only public key.
VITE_SENTRY_DSN=
# Base URL for client feedback magic-links. The "/f/<token>" path segment is
# appended by supabase/functions/_shared/magic-link.ts — set this to the app
# root ONLY (no trailing "/f"). Used by send-delivery + process-scheduled-sends
# as the Edge Function secret PUBLIC_FEEDBACK_URL_BASE in production.
VITE_FEEDBACK_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Server-side secrets — set via `npx supabase secrets set` or the dashboard.
# NEVER add these to .env.local: the Vite client bundles import.meta.env.* and
# ships it to every browser visitor, which would leak the secret.
#
# RESEND_API_KEY            Edge Function secret. Read by
#                           supabase/functions/_shared/resend.ts for delivery
#                           sends + cron-driven scheduled sends. The SAME
#                           value is reused as the Supabase Auth → SMTP
#                           password (user = "resend") so magic-link,
#                           password-reset, and signup-confirmation emails
#                           ship through Resend too.
# PDFSHIFT_API_KEY          Edge Function secret. PDF attachment rendering.
# PUBLIC_FEEDBACK_URL_BASE  Edge Function secret. Magic-link base URL for
#                           client feedback pages. Set to the app ROOT only
#                           (e.g. https://clearpressai.com) — the "/f/<token>"
#                           segment is appended by buildFeedbackUrl. A
#                           trailing "/f" here produces "/f/f/<token>" which
#                           does not match the /f/:token React Router route
#                           and renders a blank page.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY         Edge Function secret. Set since Phase 2.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
